  <brief_title>Oral Tranexamic Acid Versus Diosmin for Treatment of Menorrhagia in Women Using Copper IUD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Oral Tranexamic Acid Versus Diosmin for Treatment of Menorrhagia in Women Using Copper IUD: Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
