  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the efficacy of tranexamic acid and diosmin in reducing menstrual blood loss in
      women having Intra Uterine Contraceptive Device (IUD) and suffer from menorrhagia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
